Floss your teeth once a day.

57
00:04:18,742 --> 00:04:22,076
Clean your tongue at least once a day.

58
00:04:22,076 --> 00:04:26,569
Visit your dentist once in every 6 months.

59
00:04:26,570 --> 00:04:32,810
用法比较：表示重复活动的一般现在时态和现在完成进行时态

60
00:04:32,810 --> 00:04:35,410
在来比较下面两个句子：

61
00:04:35,410 --> 00:04:37,556
例句1）I swim

62
00:04:37,557 --> 00:04:41,303
1000 meters every afternoon.

63
00:04:41,303 --> 00:04:47,050
例句2）I have been swimming 1000 meters every afternoon.

64
00:04:47,051 --> 00:04:56,331
